Privacy Policy for Jame Sindhi

Effective Date: 16/02/2025

Welcome to Jame Sindhi. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you
use our mobile application ("App").

1. Information We Collect

We collect the following types of information to improve our services and provide a better experience:

1.1 Personal Information

Firebase Authentication may collect your email address for login purposes.

1.2 Device & Usage Data

Device Information: Android Advertising ID (AAID) for personalized ads.

App Usage Data: We collect data on interactions with in-app content and advertisements.

Network Information: Internet connection status for app functionality.

1.3 Media & Storage Permissions

The app may request access to storage (READ/WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE) to save or display images and files.

2. How We Use Your Information

We use your data for:

Providing and improving the App's features.

Displaying relevant ads via Meta Audience Network.

Storing and managing user data through Firebase Database & Firebase Storage.

Ensuring app security and preventing fraud.

3. Data Sharing & Third-Party Services

We do not sell or rent your data. However, we integrate third-party services that may collect user data:

3.1 Meta Audience Network

Used for displaying ads.

Collects device identifiers (AAID), app interactions, and ad engagement data.

More info: Meta Audience Network Privacy Policy

3.2 Firebase Services

Firebase Authentication: Manages user login.

Firebase Database & Storage: Stores user-generated data.

More info: Firebase Privacy Policy

4. Data Security

We implement security measures to protect user data. However, no method is 100% secure. Users should take precautions when sharing personal information.

5. Data Retention & Deletion

We retain data as long as necessary for app functionality.

You can request data deletion by contacting us at: kalwarshafqat78@gmail.com.

Alternatively, submit a request using this form: https://forms.gle/yNFuEmuoaDuoJa7n9

6. User Rights & Choices

You can opt out of personalized ads by adjusting your device settings.

You may revoke storage access permissions via Android Settings.

7. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Changes will be posted within the App.

8. Contact Us

